       acc-cod-vt2-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Pre-accettazione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-pie-tra-cur (1)    not  = 30
                     go to acc-cod-vt2-999.
           if        w-pie-cod-vet (1)    =    zero
                     go to acc-cod-vt2-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
